<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=The_Guardian&action=edit&section=30.php.html" title="Edit section: Regular cartoon strips">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Regular_cartoon_strips">Regular cartoon strips</span></h3>
