<li><a href="John_Edward_Taylor" title="John Edward Taylor">Edward Taylor</a> (1861–1872)</li>
<li><a href="Charles_Prestwich_Scott" title="Charles Prestwich Scott" class="mw-redirect">Charles Prestwich Scott</a> (1872–1929)</li>
<li><a href="Edward_Taylor_Scott" title="Edward Taylor Scott">Ted Scott</a> (1929–1932)</li>
<li><a href="William_Percival_Crozier" title="William Percival Crozier">William Percival Crozier</a> (1932–1944)</li>
<li>Alfred Powell Wadsworth (1944–1956)</li>
<li><a href="Alastair_Hetherington" title="Alastair Hetherington">Alastair Hetherington</a> (1956–1975)</li>
